 You can retrieve session recording data using the following code:
```javascript
const sessionId = 'fef4db93-9995-4147-be1c-27ebb0228ea6';
const browserbase = new Browserbase();
const data = await browserbase.getSessionRecording(sessionId);
```

 You would use the following code snippet: 
```javascript
import { BrowserbaseLoader } from 'langchain/document_loaders/web/browserbase.js'; 
const loader = new BrowserbaseLoader(['https://example.com'], { textContent: true }); 
const docs = await loader.load();
```
